Build
=====

0) Update repository's Git submodules

1) Install required libraries
	- Boost 1.55
	- Urbi SDK (dev version from Github)
	- rapidjson 0.11 (header only)

2) Create symlinks to installed libraries
	- 3rd-party/boost -> BOOST_ROOT
	- 3rd-party/urbi -> UrbiÂ SDK
	- 3rd-paty/rapidjson -> rapidjson's include dir

3) Build onboard (in 'onboard/build')
	- run `cmake ../src && make`

Run
===
In onboard directory run
	`urbi-launch -s build/xcs/urbi/Xci.uob/libuxci.so build/xcs/urbi/json.uob/libujson.so -- -f src/demo.u -i`

urbi-launch must be in PATH and libboost must be in LD_LIBRARY_PATH,
optionally source 'env' file in onboard directory.

